Supplemental Privacy Notice
English
ESPAÑOL / SPANISH
FRANÇAIS / FRENCH
Last updated September 27, 2022 – Version 1.0
This Supplemental Privacy Notice (this “Notice”) applies to users who complete our lead form and download content through our “You Can” campaign, and is intended to supplement Subsplash’s (“Subsplash,” “We” or “Us”) privacy policy (the “Privacy Policy”) found here or at
https://www.subsplash.com/legal/privacy
. In the event of conflict between the Privacy Policy and this Notice, this Notice takes precedence.
DATA SHARING
For those who complete our lead form and download content through our “You Can” campaign, we may share certain personal information (as defined in the Privacy Policy) with our partner organizations for marketing purposes. We have shared the following categories of personal information with our partner organizations through this program:
Identifiers: Name, email address;
Characteristics of protected classifications under California or federal law: Religious affiliation and attendance;
Commercial Information: Products and/or services purchased;
Professional or employment-related information: Employer
WHEN AND WHY WE COLLECT YOUR DATA
We collect this data when you fill out a lead form; some of the data is already provided to us
through your Subsplash account.
We collect and use the data described in this section, in addition to other uses described in our
Privacy Policy, to facilitate the use of the lead form you filled out and operate with our
marketing partners. This allows us to inform you of products and services of Subsplash or our
partners that may be of interest to you.
OPT OUT
If you wish to opt-out of information sharing through this program, please
click here
. Alternatively, you can contact us at:
privacy@subsplash.com
.
CONTACT US
If you have any questions or concerns about our use of data through this program, please contact
us at:
privacy@subsplash.com
.
